quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  7,74,"Futhi khumbulani ngesikhathi enenza ukuthi nibe ngabalandelayo emva kuka-A’d futhi wanizinzisa emhlabeni, nakha izindlu ezinkulu zobukhosi kalula naqopha izintaba (nakha) izindlu ngakho-ke khumbulani ububele bukaMvelinqangi futhi ningenzi ukona ezweni"
  7,75,"Bathi abaholi balabo ababeqhosha phakathi kwabantu bakhe kulabo ababebuthakathaka kulabo ababekholwa phakathi kwabo ngakube niyazi ukuthi uSalih uthunywe yiNkosi yakhe na? Bathi, “ngempela thina singabakholwayo kulokho athunywe nako”"
  7,76,"Labo ababeqhosha bathi, “Ngempela thina asikholwa kulokho enikukholwayo”"
  7,77,"Ngakho-ke balibulala ikameli eliyinsikazi bawudelela umthetho weNkosi yabo futhi bathi, “Oh Salih! Silethele lokho osisongela ngako uma ungomunye wezithunywa”"
  7,78,Ngakho-ke bathathwa ukuzamazama komhlaba basala (befile) emakhaya abo bebhumbuluzile
  7,79,"Ngakho-ke (uSalih) wabafulathela wathi, “Oh Bantu bami! Nginitshenile umyalezo weNkosi yami futhi nganinika iseluleko esihle kepha anibathandi abeluleki abahle”"
  7,80,Futhi (khumbula) ngesikhathi uLothi ethi kubantu bakhe “ngakube nenza ukona okungakaze kwenziwe ngisho noyedwa ngaphambilini emhlabeni na
  7,81,Ngempela nina nikhanukela abesilisa esikhundleni sabesifazane manje nina ningabantu abeqa imithetho